description:
The doc is back! Bunnie welcomes back the highly requested Dr. Cherise Felix, MD. to give an update on all the offerings at her Service Station including injections for men and beautiful buttholes. "Surgery is not the whole answer."  - Bunnie 
"I feel like vaginas can take a beating." - Bunnie 
 
Dr. Felix: cherisefelixmd.com
